description: Daniels Corporate Advisory Company, Inc. acquires, refurbishes, advertises, add location electronics, leases, and sells commercial vehicles to independent drivers and operators in the United States. It also provides corporate financial consulting and merchant banking services, as well as creates and implements corporate strategy alternatives for the mini-cap public and private company clients. Daniels Corporate Advisory Company, Inc. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Forest Hills, New York.
